---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about the Freedom Factory in Bradenton, FL — originally built in the early 1970s as Desoto Speedway and revived by Cleetus McFarland."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">The Track</div>
      <h1>About Freedom Factory</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container about-inner">
      <div class="about-main">
        <h2>A Legend Reborn</h2>
        <p>
          The world-famous Freedom Factory is located at 21050 FL-64 in
          Bradenton, Florida, owned by well-known YouTuber and car enthusiast
          Cleetus McFarland. What you see today started life in the early 1970s
          as Desoto Speedway.
        </p>

        <p>
          The 3/8-mile asphalt oval, with 12-degree banking through the turns,
          quickly became known as the fastest 3/8-mile speedway in the South.
          Being one of the most popular race tracks in the state, it saw many
          NASCAR legends and circle track icons compete on its asphalt.
        </p>

        <p>
          After many decades of success, the track unfortunately closed down and
          went quiet for years. Then Cleetus McFarland — whose YouTube channel
          has grown into one of the largest automotive channels in the world —
          had a vision.
        </p>

        <p>
          A second life has been given to a beloved track enriched with racing
          history, and we are very proud to share it with everyone. The Freedom
          Factory now hosts some of the most unique, entertaining, and downright
          wild motorsport events you'll find anywhere in America.
        </p>

        <blockquote>"We hope to see you all at an event."</blockquote>

        <h3>The Track Facts</h3>
        <div class="fact-table">
          <div class="fact-row">
            <span>Distance</span><span>3/8 Mile (0.375 mi)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row"><span>Surface</span><span>Asphalt</span></div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <span>Banking</span><span>12 Degrees</span>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <span>Configuration</span><span>Oval</span>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <span>Originally Built</span><span>Early 1970s</span>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <span>Original Name</span><span>Desoto Speedway</span>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <span>Current Owner</span><span>Cleetus McFarland</span>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <span>Address</span><span>21050 FL-64, Bradenton, FL 34212</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h4>Come Race With Us</h4>
          <p>
            Interested in competing at Freedom Factory? Check out our competitor
            hub for class rules, registration info, and everything you need to
            get on track.
          </p>
          <a href="/competitors" class="btn btn-red">Competitor Hub →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h4>Get Tickets</h4>
          <p>
            Spectator tickets for all 2026 events are available online.
            Experience the fastest 3/8-mile oval in the South in person.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://tickets.thefoat.com/FreedomFactory"
            class="btn btn-yellow"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener">Buy Tickets →</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h4>Follow the Action</h4>
          <p>
            Follow Freedom Factory USA on social media for race updates,
            results, and behind-the-scenes content.
          </p>
          <div class="social-group">
            <a
              href="https://www.youtube.com/c/SPOCARVideos"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="social-btn">YouTube</a
            >
            <a
              href="https://www.facebook.com/FreedomFactory1"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="social-btn">Facebook</a
            >
            <a
              href="https://www.instagram.com/freedom.factoryusa/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="social-btn">Instagram</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--ff-dark-2), var(--ff-black));
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    padding: 64px 0 48px;
  }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(56px, 8vw, 100px);
    color: var(--ff-white);
  }

  .about-section {
    padding: var(--section-pad) 0;
  }
  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-main h2 {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 52px);
    color: var(--ff-white);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .about-main p {
    color: var(--ff-light-gray);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-main h3 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 40px);
    color: var(--ff-white);
    margin: 40px 0 20px;
  }

  blockquote {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--ff-primary);
    padding: 16px 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    background: var(--ff-dark-2);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    font-family: var(--font-condensed);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ff-light-gray);
  }

  .fact-table {
    background: var(--ff-dark-2);
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .fact-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .fact-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .fact-row span:first-child {
    font-family: var(--font-condensed);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ff-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .fact-row span:last-child {
    color: var(--ff-white);
    font-family: var(--font-condensed);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--ff-dark-2);
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .sidebar-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-condensed);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ff-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .sidebar-card p {
    color: var(--ff-gray);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .btn-red {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-condensed);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--ff-primary);
    color: white;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-red:hover {
    background: var(--ff-primary-dark);
  }

  .social-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .social-btn {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-condensed);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px;
    background: var(--ff-dark-3);
    border: 1px solid #444;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    color: var(--ff-light-gray);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .social-btn:hover {
    background: var(--ff-primary);
    color: white;
    border-color: var(--ff-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .fact-row {
      grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
